About us

In 1928, A.A. Milne gifted the world with “The House at Pooh Corner,” a literary treasure that introduced us to Tigger and reacquainted us with the charming world of Winnie-the-Pooh and his dear friends. For generations, these tales have been a source of comfort, laughter, and learning for both children and adults alike.

As the clock chimed midnight on January 1, 2024, this masterpiece, along with other cultural gems from the same year, gracefully entered the public domain.

The legacy

With WINNIE, we aim to honor the legacy of A.A. Milne’s timeless classic and the joy it has brought to readers of all ages. As Tigger first bounded onto the scene with his irrepressible energy, WINNIE leaps into the world of cryptocurrency with a heart full of nostalgia and a mission to spread positivity.

WINNIE is more than just a cryptocurrency; it’s a celebration of the simple pleasures, the adventures sought in the thicket of the woods, and the lessons learned in the warmth of companionship. It’s about the laughter shared over a jar of honey and the comfort of knowing that you have friends who care.

As we embark on this new journey with WINNIE, we invite you to join us in rekindling those cherished childhood memories. Together, let’s create a community that values kindness, friendship, and the joyous curiosity of exploring our own Hundred Acre Woods in the vast expanse of the digital world.

Get ready to be part of the next chapter where every transaction is a step back to the days of innocence and every coin is a token of the stories that once filled our hearts.
